<h1>Memphis Pack</h1>
<p class="lead">Bold flat colour, geometric surface patterns on every face, hard drop shadows, zigzag borders, and anti-functionalist ornament. Inspired by the Memphis Group (Milan, 1981&ndash;88).</p>

<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr><th>Type</th><td>Full (theme + effects)</td></tr>
