<section>
  <h2>What's Included</h2>

  <h3>Pattern System</h3>
  <p>18 CSS custom properties for pure-CSS geometric patterns. The heart of Memphis design.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Stripes</strong>: <code>--m-pat-stripe-y</code>, <code>-p</code>, <code>-b</code>, <code>-t</code>, <code>-vert</code> (diagonal + vertical)</li>
    <li><strong>Polka dots</strong>: <code>--m-pat-dots-y</code>, <code>-r</code>, <code>-b</code>, <code>-p</code>, <code>-sm</code>, <code>-lg</code></li>
    <li><strong>Checkerboard</strong>: <code>--m-pat-check-sm</code>, <code>-md</code>, <code>-y</code>, <code>-p</code></li>
    <li><strong>Crosshatch</strong>: <code>--m-pat-cross</code></li>
    <li><strong>Zigzag</strong>: <code>--m-pat-zigzag-y</code>, <code>-b</code></li>
    <li><strong>Squiggle</strong>: <code>--m-pat-squiggle-r</code>, <code>-b</code>, <code>-p</code>, <code>-bk</code> (SVG data URIs)</li>
    <li><strong>Confetti</strong>: <code>--m-pat-confetti</code> (layered radial gradients)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Typography</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Display</strong>: Boogaloo &mdash; geometric rounded boldness (single weight)</li>
    <li><strong>Body</strong>: Outfit (400, 700, 900) &mdash; clean geometric sans</li>
    <li><strong>Mono</strong>: Space Mono (400, 700) &mdash; typewriter/plotter aesthetic</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Effects</h3>
  <p>Opt-in decorative CSS effects via <code>data-effect</code> attributes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>data-effect="memphis-zigzag"</code> &mdash; 16px zigzag pattern band with borders</li>
    <li><code>data-effect="memphis-dots"</code> &mdash; 24px polka dot pattern band</li>
    <li><code>data-effect="memphis-stripe"</code> &mdash; 12px diagonal stripe band</li>
    <li><code>data-effect="memphis-confetti"</code> &mdash; confetti pattern overlay</li>
    <li><code>data-effect="memphis-squiggle"</code> &mdash; squiggle pattern background</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Usage</h2>

{% set patternCode %}<style>
  .hero-banner {
    background: var(--m-pat-dots-r);
    background-color: var(--m-cream);
    border: 2.5px solid var(--m-black);
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--m-black);
    padding: 2rem;
  }
</style>{% endset %}

  <code-block language="css" label="Using pattern tokens">{{ patternCode | escape }}</code-block>

{% set bandCode %}<div data-effect="memphis-zigzag" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div data-effect="memphis-dots" data-color="blue" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div data-effect="memphis-stripe" data-color="pink" aria-hidden="true"></div>{% endset %}

  <code-block language="html" label="Decorative band dividers">{{ bandCode | escape }}</code-block>

{% set cardCode %}<article style="
  border: 2.5px solid var(--m-black);
